  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Due to the lack of other drugs to treat gastroparesis Janssen and FDA approved the
      compassionate use of cisapride to treat patients who had no other effective therapy. For this
      observational study, 3 patients who had already been prescribed cisapride by outside
      physicians, were followed to determine the effectiveness of cisapride on their gastric
      emtpying.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
